p: Transmissible gastroenteritis coronavirus - TGEV (vaccine strain h-5; Nisseiken, Tokyo, Japan) was propagated in Vero cells; porcine reproductive and respiratory syndrome virus - PRRSV (live PRRS vaccine - Ingelvac PRRS® MLV- Boehringer Ingelheim company); Japanese Encephalitis virus – JEV and Getal virus - GV (live vaccine – Kyoto Biken company, Kyoto, Japan).
